{"type":"message","id":"455ddb9b","parentId":"29711420","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:49:04.657Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 00:49 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态：企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务。搜索近期的最新资讯，整理3-5条关键信息，保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}],"timestamp":1774716544647}}
{"type":"message","id":"91fa6cf7","parentId":"455ddb9b","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:49:10.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for the latest news about enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services. I'll use web search to find relevant industry trends and then compile 3-5 key pieces of information to save to the notes file.","thinkingSignature":"c4546d5346ceba74f48b5e3d079c395db6a367a74b73252e6d2a3ab242e146e7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qg0c3e5nw1og_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qg0c3e5nw1og_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent && cat skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42026,"totalTokens":42282,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001668,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00504312,"total":0.0052450199999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774716544654}}
